      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">考槃.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>考槃在澗，碩人之寬，獨寐寤言，永矢弗諼。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He has reared his hut by the stream in the valley,
That large man, so much at his ease.
Alone he sleeps, and wakes, and talks.
He swears he will never forget his true joy.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
