      <prop type="x-translation-ref">考槃.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>考槃在阿，碩人之薖，獨寐寤歌，永矢弗過。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He has reared his hut in the bend of the mound,
That large man, with such an air of indifference.
Alone, he sleeps and wakes, and sings.
He swears he will never pass from this spot.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
