      <prop type="x-translation-ref">考槃.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>考槃在陸，碩人之軸，獨寐寤宿，永矢弗告。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He has reared his hut on the level height,
That large man, so self-collected.
Alone, he sleeps and wakes, and sleeps again.
He swears he will never tell of his delight.</seg>
